WEBVTT

00:01.140 --> 00:02.492
Previously on Greenleaf.

00:02.578 --> 00:04.148
Gentlemen to what do I
owe you this pleausre.

00:04.187 --> 00:06.263
And if it has anything
to do with that police officer,

00:06.265 --> 00:08.054
David Nelson, I can't help you.

00:08.117 --> 00:10.050
The senate is launching
an inquiry, James,

00:10.052 --> 00:12.085
into whether your church
and others like it

00:12.087 --> 00:14.688
are taking advantage
of your tax-exempt status.

00:14.690 --> 00:15.922
Where's Basie Skanks?

00:15.924 --> 00:17.657
One of the cops
who works around here told me

00:17.659 --> 00:21.479
about a 15-year-old girl
from the church.

00:22.464 --> 00:24.231
Nothin' happened to Danielle.

00:24.233 --> 00:25.499
I don't know what you're talkin' about.

00:25.501 --> 00:27.534
I know that she changed her story.

00:27.536 --> 00:29.469
Leave my family alone.

00:29.471 --> 00:30.704
He never did anything.

00:30.706 --> 00:32.238
So why did you say he raped you?

00:32.241 --> 00:35.675
Tell that little side piece
to stop textin' so damn much.

00:35.677 --> 00:36.810
How did you two meet?

00:36.812 --> 00:38.011
On our way to dinner,

00:38.013 --> 00:40.547
he pulled over
and asked me to marry him.

00:40.549 --> 00:41.648
We need to get help.

00:41.650 --> 00:43.850
- Like what, therapy?
- Yes.

00:43.852 --> 00:45.919
- Got some big news last night.
- Yeah, what about?

00:45.921 --> 00:47.487
Charity and I are havin' a baby.

00:47.489 --> 00:50.424
You said at dinner the day
that we buried faith

00:50.426 --> 00:52.325
that David Nelson never contacted you.

00:52.327 --> 00:53.827
He hadn't, as far as I know.

00:53.829 --> 00:55.996
I found a message on my phone
this morning from him saying

00:55.998 --> 00:58.065
that he tried reaching you
over and over again.

00:58.067 --> 00:59.867
- So, what do you want me to do?
- Nothin'.

01:01.170 --> 01:02.335
Pastor Greenleaf?

01:04.840 --> 01:06.206
Back the blue, huh?

01:06.208 --> 01:07.507
You could call it whatever you want.

01:07.509 --> 01:08.809
That was just the mayor's suggestion.

01:08.811 --> 01:11.445
What matters to him is
that at least one black church

01:11.447 --> 01:12.612
in Memphis show some support

01:12.614 --> 01:14.481
for the police in the midst of all this.

01:14.483 --> 01:15.749
And you're approaching calvary

01:15.751 --> 01:18.385
- because Nelson is on the roll?
- That's correct.

01:18.387 --> 01:20.520
We're not asking you
to honor officer Nelson

01:20.522 --> 01:21.688
specifically, of course.

01:21.690 --> 01:23.890
But if you could honor
the force in general

01:23.892 --> 01:25.492
and he could attend, well,

01:25.494 --> 01:26.793
the message would be clear enough

01:26.795 --> 01:28.428
for our purposes, anyway.

01:29.698 --> 01:31.531
You knew this is
what he'd come in here for?

01:31.533 --> 01:32.405
Mm.

01:36.902 --> 01:40.104
As I'm sure you know, bishop,
Triumph Church

01:40.106 --> 01:43.273
is hosting this protest
scheduled Friday night.

01:43.275 --> 01:44.942
That boy's mother wasn't even a member

01:44.944 --> 01:46.510
till after that boy was killed.

01:46.512 --> 01:47.911
We heard that as well.

01:47.913 --> 01:49.847
And I heard the Skanks went to her house

01:49.849 --> 01:51.448
and invited her personally.

01:51.450 --> 01:53.524
I believe that is correct.

01:54.620 --> 01:55.948
You don't find that cynical?

01:56.655 --> 01:58.655
The mayor doesn't find this cynical?

01:58.657 --> 02:00.357
The mayor thought, bishop,

02:00.359 --> 02:01.859
since pastor Skanks has made a point

02:01.861 --> 02:03.260
of calling you out publicly

02:03.262 --> 02:06.430
for not yet taking a stand
for or against David Nelson,

02:06.432 --> 02:08.699
you might see some advantage in this.

02:08.701 --> 02:10.317
Not enough of one yet.

02:11.370 --> 02:13.871
The mayor thought
that might be your assessment.

02:13.873 --> 02:15.363
So...

02:16.609 --> 02:17.868
And this is what?

02:18.577 --> 02:22.846
A plat map of Calvary's property
and the adjoining lot,

02:22.848 --> 02:25.749
currently held in trust
by Memphis redevelopment.

02:25.751 --> 02:27.751
They have an offer on the table.

02:27.753 --> 02:30.220
But I know Calvary's expressed
an interest in the past

02:30.222 --> 02:32.589
for a pool and community
center, I think.

02:32.591 --> 02:34.124
And the city said no.

02:34.126 --> 02:36.948
And the city is prepared
to change its mind,

02:37.630 --> 02:42.966
which makes this, we think,
a very exciting time.

02:45.571 --> 02:47.638
This Sunday would be great.

02:50.643 --> 02:52.029
Gentlemen.

02:52.945 --> 02:54.344
[Door opens]

02:55.981 --> 02:58.820
Basie Skanks ain't got no pool.

02:59.418 --> 03:02.126
No. He doesn't.

