03:07.626 --> 03:09.059
♪ all right ♪

03:09.061 --> 03:10.627
♪ baby ♪

03:10.629 --> 03:13.297
♪ uh-huh ♪

03:13.299 --> 03:15.732
♪ uh-huh ♪

03:18.804 --> 03:20.337
♪ well ♪

03:23.676 --> 03:26.810
♪ uh-huh ♪

03:26.812 --> 03:32.182
♪ ooh, ooh, ooh, ooh ♪

03:32.184 --> 03:34.084
♪ baby, baby ♪
♪ oh ♪

03:38.591 --> 03:40.791
♪ baby ♪

