03:49.468 --> 03:51.768
- get that out to Dave, okay?
- Mm-hmm.

03:51.770 --> 03:55.472
All right. Ah, the woman at the well.

03:55.474 --> 03:57.474
Go ahead, Daddy. Tell me my life.

03:57.476 --> 04:00.878
It's about to get better.
I gave some more thought

04:00.880 --> 04:02.846
about what you said
about officer Nelson.

04:03.249 --> 04:04.248
- Really?
- Give him a call.

04:04.250 --> 04:05.891
Have him come in.

04:06.852 --> 04:08.752
W... what changed your mind?

04:08.754 --> 04:11.822
Where were you when I laid
The Earth's foundations?

04:11.824 --> 04:13.300
Just have him come in.

04:13.926 --> 04:15.292
Today, if possible.

04:18.497 --> 04:20.293
You don't seem to want to be here.

04:21.300 --> 04:22.397
Am I wrong?

04:23.302 --> 04:24.220
Nope.

04:25.037 --> 04:27.325
But you came to therapy anyway.

04:27.773 --> 04:28.607
Why?

04:29.475 --> 04:31.175
Because she would have made
my life a livin' hell

04:31.177 --> 04:32.247
if I didn't.

04:33.710 --> 04:34.759
You just can't seem to agree

04:34.761 --> 04:36.761
about what kind
of a relationship you wanna have

04:36.763 --> 04:38.736
while you stay married.

04:40.136 --> 04:41.904
So, what's the essential problem?

04:43.788 --> 04:44.860
Other women.

04:45.804 --> 04:46.738
He knows I know.

04:46.740 --> 04:48.892
And I know he knows I know. So...

04:52.372 --> 04:54.179
You have extramarital affairs?

04:56.984 --> 04:58.789
I'll take that as a yes.

04:59.428 --> 05:00.885
So, why do you do that?

05:04.091 --> 05:05.657
Answer the question, Jacob.

